OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778958675
OL,3,CTeacher jailed for taking millions of
OL,4,Cupskirt images of pupils with 'spy pen'
OL,6,FA former high school teacher has been
OL,7,Fjailed for taking more than a million
OL,8,Fupskirt pictures of his pupils using
OL,9,Fsecret cameras hidden in "spy pens".
OL,11,FMatthew Gilkes, from Chorley, used the
OL,12,Fspy pens along with tiny cube cameras
OL,13,Fto take indecent images of his pupils
OL,14,Fwhile teaching ICT at a Greater
OL,15,FManchester High School.
OL,17,FThe 47-year-old also posed online as a
OL,18,Fteenage boy to groom "a large number"
OL,19,Fof underage girls and pressure them
OL,20,Finto sending images.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
