FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778958675
OL,3,CTeacher jailed for taking millions of
OL,4,Cupskirt images of pupils with 'spy pen'
OL,6,FGilkes' crimes were unmasked when he
OL,7,Fwas caught taking pictures of children
OL,8,Fat a leisure centre in Chorley in
OL,9,FAugust 2024.
OL,11,FAfter police tracked him down, a
OL,12,Fsearch of his home uncovered more than
OL,13,F80 devices including mobile phones,
OL,14,Flaptops, spy pens, and handheld
OL,15,Fcameras containing thousands of
OL,16,Findecent images of children.
OL,18,FDet Con Holly McClave and Det Con
OL,19,FRachel Phillips helped bring Gilkes to
OL,20,Fjustice. They described him as a
OL,21,F"highly dangerous man".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
