PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778958675
OL,3,CTeacher jailed for taking millions of
OL,4,Cupskirt images of pupils with 'spy pen'
OL,6,FDC McClave said: "Matthew Gilkes is a
OL,7,Fhighly dangerous man who has shown
OL,8,Fpersistent predatory behaviour towards
OL,9,Fyoung girls who he has taken advantage
OL,10,Fof, groomed and exploited for his own
OL,11,Fsexual gratification."
OL,26,@nD@ROU
