PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778958675
OL,3,CTeacher jailed for taking millions of
OL,4,Cupskirt images of pupils with 'spy pen'
OL,6,FGilkes, formerly of Harrison Road,
OL,7,FChorley pleaded guilty in November
OL,8,F2025 to 42 charges including operating
OL,9,Fequipment beneath clothing of another
OL,10,Fwithout consent, commonly known as
OL,11,Fupskirting, engaging in sexual
OL,12,Fcommunication with a child, indecent
OL,13,Fimages of children offences and
OL,14,Fcausing or inciting a girl aged 13 to
OL,15,F15 to engage in sexual activity.
OL,17,FHe appeared at Preston Crown Court
OL,18,Fwhere he was jailed for 16 years with
OL,19,Fan additional five year licence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
