PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778958675
OL,3,CTeacher jailed for taking millions of
OL,4,Cupskirt images of pupils with 'spy pen'
OL,6,FHe was also given an indefinite sexual
OL,7,Fharm prevention order.
OL,9,FDC McClave added: "The victims in this
OL,10,Fcase have shown incredible bravery in
OL,11,Fspeaking about what happened to them
OL,12,Fand I commend them for their courage.
OL,13,FI hope this sentence gives them some
OL,14,Fsense that justice has been done.
OL,16,F"We will continue to target those who
OL,17,Fexploit and abuse young people, we
OL,18,Fwill listen to victims, and we will do
OL,19,Fall we can to put offenders before the
OL,20,Fcourts, as we have done here."
OL,26,@qD@SOUxD@AOU|D@^O]
